<P>
<FONT FACE="AGaramond">Each of these assignments is due by the beginning
of the discussion section on Wednesday.  This means that your electronic
submission to Checkmate (</FONT><FONT FACE="Courier New" SIZE=2>checkmate.ics.uci.edu</FONT><FONT FACE="AGaramond">)
should be made before you come to section and that any paper submission
will be due at the start of class.  In general, you will use the Wednesday
and Friday lab sessions to work on each assignment, with the Monday session
to clear up any last-minute questions or problems.</FONT></P>
<P>
<FONT FACE="AGaramond">We understand that occasionally, scheduling constraints
will keep you from submitting your assignment electronically before the
start of Wednesday&#39;s section and you&#39;ll need to use Checkmate at
the beginning of your lab section; we won&#39;t penalize you if this happens
once or twice, but we expect that you will use your Wednesday lab time to
start work on the new assignment, not to finish up the previous one.</FONT></P>
